data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch home in Elysian Fields.  Upon entering, you'll enjoy the vaulted living room and dining room with huge sun-filled windows.  It is an open floor plan between the kitchen, living room, dining room, and family room areas.  A large primary bedroom with a bathroom suite that includes a double sink vanity and bath. Two extra bedrooms and full bathroom.    Laundry/mud room complete with washer/dryer and space for cubbies!  Finished basement with large recreation area, 4th bedroom and full bathroom.  Beautiful back yard with large deck and views of the golf course!  Close to shopping, dining, recreational parks and the Interstate.
